{"tid":576672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你連DSE Oral都講唔贏自修生，你入倒大學都係廢柴，係loser","createTime":"2018-03-01T05:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T13:15:53.000Z","uid":108201,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"29131999de7068f66d76899117e5282d598fce65","tid":576672,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:41:34.000Z","msg":"睇見班19 DSE中學雞話我哋去搞事，去令佢哋入唔倒大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟想當年中文會考高考Oral，UE Oral都同高齡自修生一齊小組討論，只要有論點論據，言之成理咪一樣拎A，我哋點令你哋班中學雞入唔倒大學呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你哋中學雞咁驚嘅就強化下自己中英文水平，我哋高齡&ldquo;自修生&rdquo;已經無操卷咁多年，咁都高分唔過我哋就不如唔好入大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n與其你入到去都係講唔贏班老鬼，比班莊嘅老鬼/大學制度玩到你反皮，不如你就quit DSE算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：中英會考 高考Oral Straight A，大學上莊做P時推翻D On 9老鬼莊會制度，見班中學雞咁無信心，想屌醒佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e435e9e7c32e61eea8a0004db0c54728dd6174","tid":576672,"uid":88723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"想受惠今次財政好簡單<br />\n開Oral班打響旗號「針對性應付白撞自修生」<br />\n就可以cap番一筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea9ba1cc4953c41174dcb0459bcb9ade3a81023","tid":576672,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"51e435e9e7c32e61eea8a0004db0c54728dd6174","tid":576672,"uid":88723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"想受惠今次財政好簡單<br />\n開Oral班打響旗號「針對性應付白撞自修生」<br />\n就可以cap番一筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"其實名校之間一向有搞聯校 Oral 練習，只係好多學生以為自己好勁，無去練下就考<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你同唔同人練過先知考試時用咩Oral戰術最好最易令自己高分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}